quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  2,142,"ahmaq log kahin ge ke musalman jis qble par ( pehlay se chalay atay ) they ( ab ) is se kyun munh phair baithy. tum keh do ke mashriq aur maghrib sab khuda hi ka hai. woh jis ko chahta hai, seedhay raste par chalata hai"
  2,143,"aur isi terhan hum ne tum ko amtِ motadil banaya hai, taakay tum logon par gawah bano aur paighambar ( aakhir uz zamaan ) tum par gawah banin. aur jis qble par tum ( pehlay ) they, is ko hum ne is liye muqarrarkiya tha ke maloom karen, kon ( hamaray ) paighambar ka tabay rehta hai, aur kon ultay paon phir jata hai. aur yeh baat ( yani tehweel qibla logon ko ) giran maloom hui, magar jin ko khuda ne hadaayat bakhsh ( woh usay giran nahi samajte ) aur khuda aisa nahi ke tumahray imaan ko yuhin kho day. khuda to logon par bara meharban ( aur ) sahib rehmat hai"
  2,144,"( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum tumhara aasman ki taraf munh phair phair kar dekhna dekh rahay hain. so hum tum ko isi qble ki taraf jis ko tum pasand karte ho, munh karne ka hukum den ge to apna munh masjid haraam ( yani Khana kaaba ) ki taraf phair lau. aur tum log jahan howa karo, ( namaz parhnay ke waqt ) isi masjid ki taraf munh kar liya karo. aur jin logon ko kitaab di gayi hai, woh khoob jantay hain ke ( naya qibla ) un ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se haq hai. aur jo kaam yeh log karte hain, khuda un se be khabar nahi"
  2,145,"aur agar tum un ehley kitaab ke paas tamam nishanain bhi le kar aao, to bhi yeh tumahray qble ki pairwi nah karen. aur tum bhi un ke qble ki pairwi karne walay nahi ho. aur un mein se bhi baaz baaz ke qble ke pairo nahi. aur agar tum bawajood is ke ke tumahray paas Danish ( yani wahi khuda ) aa chuki hai, un ki khawahishon ke peechay chalo ge to zaalmon mein ( daakhil ) ho jao ge"
